</XX>
<IN>P3679 Electronic Components, NEC.
    P3714 Motor Vehicle Parts and Accessories.
    P3546 Power-Driven Handtools.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
</XX>
<TP>RES  Capital expenditures.
    PEOP  Labour.
